					<h3 >8. Encourage Others to Conserve  </h3>
					<img src="img/way8.jpg" class="img-responsive pull-left img-margin" alt="way8">
					<p>Share information about recycling and energy conservation with your friends, neighbors and co-workers, and take opportunities to encourage public officials to establish programs and policies that are good for the environment.
					Take a few minutes to contact your political representatives and the media to tell them you want immediate action on climate change. Remind them that reducing greenhouse gas emissions will also build healthier communities, spur economic innovation and create new jobs. And next time you're at the polls, vote for politicians who support effective climate policies</p>
				</div>
    		</div>
	    </div>
